snippet.title: PLUG IT IN - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Have you seen those awkwardly big chargers that just block the other outlet?! We definitely have, and we made a game about it.

Strategically position your plugs to fit in an available outlet in this juicy relaxing puzzle game! 

A Game by Sam Feng & Jose Salas
Play now on itch.io: https://unsame.itch.io/plug-it-in

#indiegame #puzzle #puzzlegame
